<div class="im-centered">
<div class="header">
	<h1>Wu Dadi 吳大帝 Sun Quan 孫權</h1>
</div>
</div>

<div class="im-centered">
<div class="row">

<div class="col-3 navigationleft">

<ul>
<li><a href="sanguo.html"><b>Three Empires</b></a></li>
	<ul>
	  <li class="navigationbar"><a href="sanguo-event.html">Previous Events</a></li>
